Fonts are loading now. The problem in the screenshot is **not font-related**.

This part:

```text
??salesPoints.heading_en_GB??
??salesPoints.title_en_GB??
??salesPoints.description_en_GB??
??salesPoints.confirm_en_GB??
```

means Spring/Thymeleaf cannot find those translation keys for the current locale, which is:

```text
en_GB
```

So your app is currently trying to load English UK messages, but you only have:

```text
messages_fr.properties
messages_nl.properties
```

## Fix 1: Add default `messages.properties`

Create this file directly under `src/main/resources`:

```text
src/main/resources/messages.properties
```

Add French fallback values:

```properties
pageTitle=Choix point de vente

salesPoints.heading=Connexion à<br>votre espace partenaire
salesPoints.title=Votre point de vente
salesPoints.description=Vous devez choisir le point de vente dans lequel vous vous trouvez actuellement.
salesPoints.confirm=Confirmer
```

This prevents `??key_en_GB??` when the browser locale is English.

